<Base
  title="How Many Cold Emails Does It Take to Get One Meeting?"
  description="With average benchmarks — 1–3% positive reply rate and roughly half of positive replies converting to meetings — expect one meeting per 100–200 well-targeted cold emails. The funnel math, step by step."
